room_title: Escape room "Close Quarters: The Purge" by Escape Game Knoxville in Knoxville
review: Had a great time! We did The Purge and it was so challenging! We didn't make it out, but we were engaged the entire time. The staff was very friendly and helpful. An overall wonderful experience! Highly recommend. I will be back for the Once Upon a Time room!!

room_title: Escape room "Close Quarters: The Purge" by Escape Game Knoxville in Knoxville
review: Tried the Purge. Didn't make it out in time, but very fun nonetheless. Love this place.

room_title: Escape room "Close Quarters: The Purge" by Escape Game Knoxville in Knoxville
review: This place is awesome! Have been here twice. We did the Villain's Lair with 10 people and The Purge with 4. It's challenging and so much fun! The owners are fantastic. Excellent customer service. Totally recommend it.
